hands_on_practices.solution:
相关定义：
$$s^2 = \frac{g_1^2}{g_1^2 + g_2^2},$$
$$\mu\frac{dg_i}{d\mu} = \frac{b_i}{16\pi^2}g_i^3
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
\mu\frac{d(g_i^2)}{d\mu}
=2g_i\,\mu\frac{dg_i}{d\mu}
=\frac{b_i}{8\pi^2}g_i^4.$$

令 $x=g_1^2$，$y=g_2^2$。则
$$s^2=\frac{x}{x+y},$$
$$\frac{\partial s^2}{\partial x}
=\frac{y}{(x+y)^2},\qquad
\frac{\partial s^2}{\partial y}
=-\frac{x}{(x+y)^2}.$$

使用链式法则，
$$\beta_{s^2}
=\mu\frac{d s^2}{d\mu}
=\frac{\partial s^2}{\partial x}\,\mu\frac{dx}{d\mu}
+\frac{\partial s^2}{\partial y}\,\mu\frac{dy}{d\mu}.$$
代入
$\mu\,dx/d\mu=(b_1/(8\pi^2))\,x^2$
与 $\mu\,dy/d\mu=(b_2/(8\pi^2))\,y^2$：
$$
\beta_{s^2}
=\frac{y}{(x+y)^2}\frac{b_1 x^2}{8\pi^2}
-\frac{x}{(x+y)^2}\frac{b_2 y^2}{8\pi^2}
=\frac{x y}{8\pi^2(x+y)^2}\bigl(b_1 x - b_2 y\bigr).
$$
换回用 $g_1,g_2$ 表示：
$$
\beta_{s^2}
=\frac{g_1^2\,g_2^2}{8\pi^2\,(g_1^2+g_2^2)^2}
\bigl(b_1\,g_1^2 - b_2\,g_2^2\bigr).
$$
